import React from 'react'
import "./input.css"


window.addEventListener("onkeydown", function(e){

  if (e.code === 13){
    console.log(e.code)
  }
})

const Input =()=> {
  return (<>
  <label>First Name
  <input className='fn'/>
  </label>

  <label>Last Name
  <input className='ln'/>
  </label>

  <label>Email
  <input className='email'/>
  </label>

  <label>Phone
  <input className='phone'/>
  </label>

  <label>Password
  <input className='password'/>
  </label>
  
  <label>Confirm Password
  <input className='confpass'/>
  </label>

  </>)
}
export default Input;
